changeSet.createView: CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW TTS_VIEW_CPXSWQR_V2 (ID, PRODUCT_PC, PRODUCT_AMOUNT, STORE_COUNT, XSSL, FREEZE_COUNT, TZSL, STATUS) AS SELECT S. ID, S.PRODUCT_PC, S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT, (S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT - XS1.XSSL - NVL(T.TZSL,0)) STORE_COUNT, XS1.XSSL XSSL, XS.XSDJSL FREEZE_COUNT, NVL(T.TZSL,0) TZSL, CASE WHEN s.status = 4 THEN '4' ELSE ( CASE WHEN (S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT - XS1.XSSL-NVL(T.TZSL,0)) = 0 THEN '3' WHEN (S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT - XS1.XSSL-NVL(T.TZSL,0)) > 0 THEN '2' WHEN S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT = (S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT - XS1.XSSL-NVL(T.TZSL,0)) THEN '1' END ) END STATUS FROM TTS_SCLTXXCJ_SCGL_V2 S INNER JOIN ( SELECT X.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID, SUM (X.SALE_AMOUNT) XSDJSL FROM TTS_SCLTXXCJ_XSDJJL_V2 X WHERE x.confirm_state = 'N' AND x.is_circulates_end = 'N' AND X.DEL_FLAG = 'N' GROUP BY PRODUCT_SCGL_ID ) XS ON XS.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID = S.PRODUCT_PC INNER JOIN ( SELECT X1.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID, SUM (X1.SALE_AMOUNT) XSSL FROM TTS_SCLTXXCJ_XSDJJL_V2 X1 WHERE X1.DEL_FLAG = 'N' GROUP BY PRODUCT_SCGL_ID ) XS1 ON XS1.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID = S.PRODUCT_PC LEFT JOIN ( SELECT R.PRODUCT_PC, SUM (R.SLAUGHTER_AMOUNT) TZSL FROM TTS_SCLTXXCJ_SLA_RECORD_V2 R WHERE R.DEL_FLAG = 'N' GROUP BY PRODUCT_PC ) T ON T .PRODUCT_PC = S.PRODUCT_PC WHERE XS.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID = XS1.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID

changeSet.createView: CREATE OR REPLACE FORCE VIEW TTS_VIEW_CPXS_V2 (ID, PRODUCT_PC, PRODUCT_AMOUNT, STORE_COUNT, XSSL, TZSL, STATUS) AS SELECT S.ID,S.PRODUCT_PC,S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT,(S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT-XS.XSSL-NVL(T.TZSL,0)) STORE_COUNT,XS.XSSL,NVL(T.TZSL,0) TZSL, case WHEN s.status = 4 then '4' else ( CASE WHEN S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT = (XS.XSSL+NVL(T.TZSL,0)) THEN '3' WHEN (S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT - XS.XSSL-NVL(T.TZSL,0)) > 0 THEN '2' WHEN S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT = (S.PRODUCT_AMOUNT - XS.XSSL-NVL(T.TZSL,0)) THEN '1' END ) end STATUS FROM TTS_SCLTXXCJ_SCGL_V2 S LEFT JOIN ( SELECT X.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID,SUM(X.SALE_AMOUNT) XSSL FROM TTS_SCLTXXCJ_XSDJJL_V2 X WHERE X.DEL_FLAG = 'N' GROUP BY PRODUCT_SCGL_ID) XS ON XS.PRODUCT_SCGL_ID = S.PRODUCT_PC LEFT JOIN ( SELECT R.PRODUCT_PC, SUM(R.SLAUGHTER_AMOUNT) TZSL FROM TTS_SCLTXXCJ_SLA_RECORD_V2 R WHERE R.DEL_FLAG = 'N' GROUP BY PRODUCT_PC ) T ON T.PRODUCT_PC = S.PRODUCT_PC
